77
00:05:04,771 --> 00:05:06,706
I'm Akiko Asagami.

78
00:05:06,706 --> 00:05:09,231
This girl's, Ms. Sara's, nanny.

79
00:05:09,809 --> 00:05:11,674
Nanny? Babysitter?

80
