who work only for noble families.

83
00:05:23,523 --> 00:05:27,482
She has both academic and physical
skills, and she is the best.

84
00:05:28,695 --> 00:05:33,632
Ms. Sara will be the eighteenth head
of the Nishikujo family.

85
00:05:34,767 --> 00:05:36,269
Nishikujo?

86
00:05:36,269 --> 00:05:38,938
The ones who used to be nobility?
Owners of the Nishikujo Concern?

87
00:05:38,938 --> 00:05:39,739
Yes!

88
00:05:39,739 --> 00:05:41,138
I don't like it.

89
00:05:42,041 --> 00:05:43,676
Ryo!

90
00:05:43,676 --> 00:05:46,946
Speaking of the Nishikujo family, the
seventeenth head of the family,

91
00:05:46,946 --> 00:05:49,506
Shigenobu Nishikujo, died
due to an illness recently.

92
00:05:49,916 --> 00:05:52,180
This is about the family's property, isn't it?


93
00:05:52,919 --> 00:05:54,354
Yes...

94
00:05:54,354 --> 00:05:57,118
I don't like it. I don't want to get involved.

95
00:05:57,790 --> 00:06:02,028
Ryo, you say that because you don't
want to guard a child, right?

96
00:06:02,028 --> 00:06:03,663
