the Hikaru Genji plan.

98
00:06:07,633 --> 00:06:09,802
You'll be kind to the child, won't you?

99
00:06:09,802 --> 00:06:13,573
She's rich, and she'll grow up
to be a beautiful woman.

100
00:06:13,573 --> 00:06:16,709
I guarantee it. Oh, what a lucky guy!

101
00:06:16,709 --> 00:06:19,371
You silly octopus. Stop talking nonsense.

102
00:06:22,648 --> 00:06:24,445
What is it? Hey?

103
00:06:36,662 --> 00:06:38,197
What is she doing?

104
00:06:38,197 --> 00:06:40,563
Her eyes, I feel that she can read my mind.

105
00:06:41,434 --> 00:06:42,401
Ms. Sara!

106
00:06:47,640 --> 00:06:51,010
Hey, Ryo, what did you do to her?
You made her cry!

107
00:06:51,010 --> 00:06:52,034
Wait!

108
00:06:53,579 --> 00:06:55,281
A lonely person,

109
00:06:55,281 --> 00:06:57,683
in a lonely world, just like being
covered with ice.

110
00:06:57,683 --> 00:07:00,652
Being alone and fighting by yourself
in a world like that.

111
00:07:01,721 --> 00:07:05,282
But the heart is very, very warm.

112
00:07:06,192 --> 00:07:07,659
Ms. Sara...

113
00:07:08,027 --> 00:07:09,892
This girl...

114
00:07:14,867 --> 00:07:18,098
Ms. Sara has a very mysterious power.

115
00:07:18,971 --> 00:07:20,573
Intuition or something like that.

116
00:07:20,573 --> 00:07:22,598
She can touch other people's minds.

117
00:07:23,276 --> 00:07:26,045
Ms. Sara has been under the
envious eyes of her relatives,

118
00:07:26,045 --> 00:07:29,537
who want to get the property,
since she was a little baby.

119
00:07:30,349 --> 00:07:34,120
Ms. Sara was raised in an atmosphere
like that, and she became sensitive,

120
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:36,884
able to feel the ugly minds
behind their smiles.

121
00:07:37,824 --> 00:07:41,726
Up until now, she has only opened up
her mind to her late father and me.

122
00:07:42,728 --> 00:07:44,525
So I was surprised to see her talking to you.

123
00:07:44,997 --> 00:07:48,067
You're the first person she's spoken to
since Mr. Shigenobu,

124
00:07:48,067 --> 00:07:50,558
her father, passed away.

125
00:07:53,506 --> 00:07:55,174
Hey, Umibozu.

126
00:07:55,174 --> 00:07:57,710
Was that true, what you told me?

127
00:07:57,710 --> 00:07:59,143
What are you talking about?

128
00:08:00,379 --> 00:08:02,615
You told me that she'll become
a beautiful woman.

129
00:08:02,615 --> 00:08:04,083
Was that true? Answer me!

130
00:08:04,083 --> 00:08:06,152
Yes, yes, she will. I'm positive!

131
00:08:06,152 --> 00:08:09,555
Good! I can't lose with Umibozu.

132
00:08:09,555 --> 00:08:12,058
Hikaru Genji Plan, now in action!

133
00:08:12,058 --> 00:08:15,892
I accept this client!

134
00:08:17,864 --> 00:08:20,662
Oh, my goodness! What a mess!

135
