Ms. Sara to live in.

136
00:08:24,904 --> 00:08:26,973
It usually looks a little bit better than this.

137
00:08:26,973 --> 00:08:28,441
Excuse me, Ms. Akiko.

138
00:08:28,441 --> 00:08:30,176
