this place your hideout?

139
00:08:30,176 --> 00:08:32,512
Yes, the mansion is too dangerous.

140
00:08:32,512 --> 00:08:35,882
I don't know about that. I think this
place is more dangerous.

141
00:08:35,882 --> 00:08:37,550
What?

142
00:08:37,550 --> 00:08:41,954
