off from anywhere.

146
00:08:49,695 --> 00:08:52,932
No, what I wanted to tell you was...

147
00:08:52,932 --> 00:08:55,867
The only problem is the filthiness
of this room.

148
00:09:07,613 --> 00:09:09,682
Oh, what a good job!

149
00:09:09,682 --> 00:09:11,951
Indeed, you are the nanny for a noble family.

150
00:09:11,951 --> 00:09:13,986
Big difference from someone I know.

151
00:09:13,986 --> 00:09:15,453
I'm so sorry.

152
00:09:16,689 --> 00:09:19,025
By the way, I heard you saying
something strange,

153
00:09:19,025 --> 00:09:22,085
like accepting the clients for the
Hikaru Genji Plan or something.

154
00:09:23,963 --> 00:09:29,168
Are you intending to educate Sara now to
become your target ten years from now?

155
00:09:29,168 --> 00:09:30,570
You're silly.

156
00:09:30,570 --> 00:09:32,605
Do you think I am patient enough
to do something like that?

157
00:09:32,605 --> 00:09:34,664
It's a joke, just a joke.

158
00:09:35,274 --> 00:09:38,177
Well, no matter how it turns out,
ten years is ten years.

159
00:09:38,177 --> 00:09:40,805
For now, I guess I better take
the current mokkori.

160
00:09:43,583 --> 00:09:46,953
No, no! Don't try to read my mind now.

161
00:09:46,953 --> 00:09:50,623
Currently, in my mind, I am thinking
about the adult world.

162
00:09:50,623 --> 00:09:53,292
A kid like you shouldn't see
things like that. Right?

163
00:09:53,292 --> 00:09:54,987
Oh, I'm an airplane now!

164
00:09:56,562 --> 00:09:58,029
Idiot.

165
00:10:06,606 --> 00:10:09,575
She doesn't know I'm here. I'm going
to have mokkori secretly.

166
00:10:14,580 --> 00:10:16,207
Thanks for the snack!

167
00:10:19,819 --> 00:10:22,288
Oh, Mr. Saeba, I didn't know you were here.

168
00:10:22,288 --> 00:10:26,019
Yes, I'm here. Please hurry up
and turn the switch off.

169
00:10:28,027 --> 00:10:29,995
What are you doing, Ryo?

170
00:10:30,429 --> 00:10:34,734
Nothing, I think various things love me.

171
00:10:34,734 --> 00:10:36,929
What shall I do?

172
00:10:47,713 --> 00:10:50,249
Incredible! Shining!

173
00:10:50,249 --> 00:10:52,351
Looks like a different house.

174
00:10:52,351 --> 00:10:56,022
And the food! Indeed, she is the best nanny!

175
00:10:56,022 --> 00:10:59,592
You are the best woman among
women, the best!

176
00:10:59,592 --> 00:11:01,027
Oh, thanks.

177
00:11:01,027 --> 00:11:04,063
I'm going to fire Kaori, so would you
please work for me here?

178
00:11:04,063 --> 00:11:07,328
What the hell are you talking about?!

179
00:11:10,536 --> 00:11:13,733
Wow! I've never eaten this much
in my entire life!

180
00:11:14,106 --> 00:11:16,700
Well, are you trying to say
my cooking isn't good?

181
00:11:17,176 --> 00:11:18,344
Kaori?

182
00:11:18,344 --> 00:11:19,811
You're fired.

183
00:11:21,013 --> 00:11:21,514
You jerk!

184
