Next, the weather forecast.

194
00:11:37,797 --> 00:11:40,099
Ms. Akiko, can you explain the
kidnapping on the news?

195
00:11:40,099 --> 00:11:42,134
No way, you took her without
telling anybody?

196
00:11:42,134 --> 00:11:43,736
Of course.

197
00:11:43,736 --> 00:11:47,873
Right now, we don't know which relative
is trying to kill Ms. Sara.

198
00:11:47,873 --> 00:11:51,502
Therefore, if Ms. Sara is hiding somewhere,
I'm sure the person will start taking action.

199
00:11:52,378 --> 00:11:54,437
Of course, I know this is dangerous.

200
00:11:55,014 --> 00:11:58,074
That's why I came to you, Mr. Saeba.

201
00:12:01,287 --> 00:12:04,313
I'm impressed. You really are the best nanny.

202
00:12:05,391 --> 00:12:06,492
But...

203
00:12:06,492 --> 00:12:07,093
Kaori!

204
00:12:07,093 --> 00:12:07,993
What?

205
00:12:07,993 --> 00:12:09,255
You're fired.

206
00:12:11,831 --> 00:12:14,823
Excuse me, Akiko, but would you
please be my partner?

207
00:12:15,501 --> 00:12:18,834
I'm sorry, but I'm just a nanny.

208
00:12:19,405 --> 00:12:20,872
Just a nanny, I see.

209
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:26,742
But I feel more than that when
I see you serving Sara.

210
00:12:28,314 --> 00:12:32,184
There is no one apart from me to whom
Ms. Sara can open her mind.

211
00:12:32,184 --> 00:12:35,244
I thought I was the only one
who could save Ms. Sara.

212
00:12:49,502 --> 00:12:51,036
The time has come.

213
00:12:51,036 --> 00:12:53,239
No matter what a super nanny she is,

214
00:12:53,239 --> 00:12:55,207
I know she's sleeping deeply
at this time of the night.

215
00:12:55,708 --> 00:12:59,542
It's 2:00 AM. Now, time to
sneak into her room!

216
00:13:07,052 --> 00:13:09,384
Ms. Sara, you scared me.

217
00:13:11,257 --> 00:13:13,058
Damn...

218
00:13:13,058 --> 00:13:15,127
