my mind and finding out

219
00:13:15,127 --> 00:13:17,061
that I'm going to sneak into Akiko's room?

220
00:13:19,598 --> 00:13:21,395
What's the matter?

221
00:13:21,967 --> 00:13:23,803
I feel lonely.

222
00:13:23,803 --> 00:13:25,395
I want to be with you, please.

223
00:13:31,744 --> 00:13:33,609
I'm in trouble.

224
00:13:33,979 --> 00:13:36,072
I'm busy tonight.

225
00:13:39,652 --> 00:13:41,119
Traces of her tears.

226
00:13:41,520 --> 00:13:44,455
Her father died recently. I can understand.

227
00:13:46,358 --> 00:13:47,825
I guess I have no choice.

228
00:13:48,494 --> 00:13:52,396
I'm going to cancel the plan for
tonight, just for tonight.

229
00:14:03,742 --> 00:14:07,046
