disappeared from her bed.

230
00:14:07,046 --> 00:14:09,081
I can't believe this!

231
00:14:09,081 --> 00:14:12,744
Your Hikaru Genji Plan has become
a Lolita complex, hasn't it?!

232
00:14:15,054 --> 00:14:19,091
I'm really disappointed in you!
Die, you pervert!

233
00:14:19,091 --> 00:14:20,524
It's a big misunderstanding!

234
00:14:26,131 --> 00:14:27,967
I'm so sorry.

235
00:14:27,967 --> 00:14:30,265
I heard the true story from Ms. Sara.

236
00:14:30,769 --> 00:14:32,471
I knew something was wrong at the time.

237
00:14:32,471 --> 00:14:35,107
I know you don't have a Lolita complex.

238
00:14:35,107 --> 00:14:38,310
You're so welcome. I slept like a baby

239
00:14:38,310 --> 00:14:41,802
after I was tied up, rolled up in a
mattress and left on the roof.

240
00:14:42,214 --> 00:14:44,750
I guess it will take a while for his
mood to be back to normal.

241
00:14:44,750 --> 00:14:47,878
Well, I thought I'd go shopping
with him, but I guess not.

242
00:14:49,488 --> 00:14:51,217
Okay, I'll go with you.

243
00:14:51,557 --> 00:14:53,993
Ryo will take care of Sara while we're gone.

244
00:14:53,993 --> 00:14:54,789
No, you can't.

245
00:14:55,728 --> 00:14:57,963
If it's outside, Kaori, you won't be
able to guard her.

246
00:14:57,963 --> 00:14:59,331
I'll go. Okay?

247
00:14:59,331 --> 00:15:01,600
Yes, I understand.


248
00:15:01,600 --> 00:15:05,161
Chance, it's a chance. Just Akiko
and me, the two of us.

249
00:15:12,978 --> 00:15:15,814
Are you sure it will be all right to go
shopping, just you and him?

250
00:15:15,814 --> 00:15:18,684
I'll disguise myself so they
won't recognize me.

251
00:15:18,684 --> 00:15:20,252
Also, Mr. Saeba will be with me.

252
00:15:20,252 --> 00:15:22,955
That's the reason I'm worried.

253
00:15:22,955 --> 00:15:25,024
Are you ready? Let's go.

254
00:15:25,024 --> 00:15:28,926
Sure! Well, Ms. Kaori, please
take care of Ms. Sara.

255
00:15:31,664 --> 00:15:33,332
Who are you?

256
00:15:33,332 --> 00:15:35,061
Where did you come from?

257
00:15:35,467 --> 00:15:36,735
What's the matter, Ryo?

258
00:15:36,735 --> 00:15:39,465
This boy came from somewhere inside.

259
00:15:40,572 --> 00:15:41,941
Ms. Sara!

260
00:15:41,941 --> 00:15:43,806
It's my overalls!

261
00:15:44,410 --> 00:15:46,312
Oh, my!

262
00:15:46,312 --> 00:15:48,847
What's the matter with you putting on
an outfit like that?

263
00:15:48,847 --> 00:15:50,747
I'm going with you.

264
00:15:51,984 --> 00:15:54,753
Oh, no, no, burdensome, no.
It's dangerous. Right?

265
00:15:54,753 --> 00:15:56,880
I'm in disguise.

266
00:16:01,160 --> 00:16:02,923
Damn it!

267
00:16:03,462 --> 00:16:05,555
See you later. Be careful!

268
00:16:06,565 --> 00:16:10,331
Well, now, Ryo can't do
anything to Ms. Akiko.

269
00:16:11,003 --> 00:16:14,404
Hey, but they look like a good family.

270
00:16:16,075 --> 00:16:18,777
Family, husband and wife, a kid.

271
00:16:18,777 --> 00:16:21,837
I don't know why, but I'm getting mad.

272
00:16:22,014 --> 00:16:26,474
Famous Sake Trial
Exciting Bazaar

273
00:16:26,685 --> 00:16:28,812
This is good. Do you like this?

274
00:16:30,656 --> 00:16:32,248
Daily necessities, how about those?

275
00:16:32,658 --> 00:16:35,752
Toothbrush, cups, slippers,
and here, for Ms. Sara.

276
00:16:36,295 --> 00:16:37,763
Here, a bra!

277
00:16:37,763 --> 00:16:40,232
It was very difficult to find this small size.

278
00:16:40,232 --> 00:16:43,065
You don't need to look for this at all.

279
00:16:44,269 --> 00:16:46,362
Well, she doesn't need these yet.

280
00:16:50,209 --> 00:16:51,777
88cm, C cup.

281
00:16:51,777 --> 00:16:53,512
This design is pretty good.

282
00:16:53,512 --> 00:16:55,946
This one would probably look good on Akiko.

283
00:17:00,219 --> 00:17:01,720
Well, take those off.

284
00:17:01,720 --> 00:17:03,312
I'm going to put these on for you.

285
00:17:03,722 --> 00:17:05,553
Oh, I'm so happy.

286
00:17:07,092 --> 00:17:08,694
What is it Ms. Sara?

287
00:17:08,694 --> 00:17:10,218
Your face turned red.

288
00:17:10,963 --> 00:17:12,430
Furniture

289
00:17:12,965 --> 00:17:16,835
Excuse me, Akiko, but our bed is
too narrow so shall we buy this?

290
00:17:16,835 --> 00:17:18,303
This is very soft.

291
00:17:18,303 --> 00:17:22,364
No thank you. I like a narrow bed better than
a wide one, so the one I'm using now is fine.

292
00:17:22,641 --> 00:17:24,176
Is that so?

293
00:17:24,176 --> 00:17:27,441
That one is too narrow for us
to sleep together.

294
00:17:30,816 --> 00:17:33,152
Akiko, I'll sneak into your room to see you.

295
00:17:33,152 --> 00:17:35,279
I've been waiting for you, Ryo.

296
00:17:36,889 --> 00:17:41,258
Ms. Sara! You can't read Mr. Saeba's
mind any more! Understand?

297
00:17:42,494 --> 00:17:46,021
Wait, wait for me. What's the matter?

298
00:17:47,599 --> 00:17:49,829
What a bad disguise.

299
00:17:52,404 --> 00:17:54,929
I guess she completely hates
you now, Mr. Saeba.

300
00:17:56,775 --> 00:18:00,575
But does Sara read other people's
minds all day?

301
00:18:02,714 --> 00:18:08,153
No, if she read other people's minds all day
while she was surrounded by bad relatives,

302
00:18:08,153 --> 00:18:10,589
she would have become insane.

303
00:18:10,589 --> 00:18:15,856
So she usually closes her mind, to prevent
other people's minds from floating into hers.

304
00:18:18,330 --> 00:18:22,301
But while she is sleeping,
her mind is off guard

305
00:18:22,301 --> 00:18:24,735
and her relatives' minds float into hers.


306
00:18:25,304 --> 00:18:29,374
The reason we left the mansion was that,
the night before, she had a nightmare.

307
00:18:29,374 --> 00:18:34,179
She was very frightened, probably because
evil minds floated into hers.

308
00:18:34,179 --> 00:18:35,681
She said that she didn't want to be there,

309
00:18:35,681 --> 00:18:37,916
that somebody would kill her,
and she was so upset.

310
00:18:37,916 --> 00:18:39,685
That's why we...

311
00:18:39,685 --> 00:18:42,654
Then, have you actually been targeted?

312
00:18:42,654 --> 00:18:43,555
No.

313
00:18:43,555 --> 00:18:44,957
No?

314
00:18:44,957 --> 00:18:47,983
Then it's not certain that you were
actually targeted by someone, is it?

315
00:18:48,427 --> 00:18:50,861
Yes, Ms. Sara was in great danger.

316
00:18:52,498 --> 00:18:56,268
That night, when the master passed away,

317
00:18:56,268 --> 00:18:58,361
Ms. Sara had a very bad nightmare.

318
00:19:07,746 --> 00:19:09,407
Sara, run!

319
00:19:15,721 --> 00:19:17,621
Let me have that girl.

320
00:19:18,056 --> 00:19:19,853
Back off, both of you.

321
00:19:27,766 --> 00:19:29,233
Mr. Saeba...

322
00:19:29,801 --> 00:19:31,270
Get out of my way.

323
00:19:31,270 --> 00:19:32,999
You don't want to get hurt, do you?

324
00:19:33,572 --> 00:19:35,474
Can you see this?

325
00:19:35,474 --> 00:19:39,044
Are you showing off your Ray-Ban
sunglasses that don't fit you at all?

326
00:19:39,044 --> 00:19:40,846
You jerk!

327
00:19:40,846 --> 00:19:43,949
I guess you're not the type to understand
unless someone teaches you.

328
00:19:43,949 --> 00:19:46,110
Who, you?

329
00:19:59,765 --> 00:20:01,824
What did you say I couldn't see?

330
00:20:02,901 --> 00:20:06,029
I can only see you looking disgusting.

331
00:20:06,505 --> 00:20:07,972
What?!

332
00:20:14,513 --> 00:20:16,071
Hurry up and get in, brother!

333
00:20:20,052 --> 00:20:22,111
That was a quick getaway!

334
00:20:23,589 --> 00:20:25,056
Mr. Saeba!

335
00:20:25,457 --> 00:20:28,153
It's okay, now.

336
00:20:28,293 --> 00:20:30,062
Thank you, Mr. Saeba.

337
00:20:30,062 --> 00:20:31,529
Wow!

338
00:20:32,831 --> 00:20:34,298
Thank you, Mr. Saeba.

339
00:20:34,733 --> 00:20:35,801
No problem.

340
00:20:35,801 --> 00:20:37,402
Well, let's go back.

341
00:20:37,402 --> 00:20:39,393
I'm afraid that someone might
try to get us again.

342
00:20:41,073 --> 00:20:42,540
Is that all?

343
00:20:43,475 --> 00:20:44,772
What is it?

344
00:20:50,082 --> 00:20:51,606
Thank you, Mr. Saeba.

345
00:21:09,167 --> 00:21:12,304
I wonder what's going on
recently with Ms. Sara?

346
00:21:12,304 --> 00:21:14,873
She's very close to Mr. Saeba all the time.

347
00:21:14,873 --> 00:21:18,944
I don't think it's a problem. Since she's
not far from Ryo, it's easy to guard her.

348
00:21:18,944 --> 00:21:20,639
But it's too much.

349
00:21:21,113 --> 00:21:23,849
Ms. Sara might have fallen
in love with Mr. Saeba.

350
00:21:23,849 --> 00:21:24,916
No way!

351
00:21:24,916 --> 00:21:27,519
Yes, kids these days mature at an early age.

352
00:21:27,519 --> 00:21:30,010
She's eleven and this is her first love.
It's late for her age.

353
00:21:30,389 --> 00:21:33,759
I'm sure she's playing baby to Ryo,
just like her father.

354
00:21:33,759 --> 00:21:35,750
Does he look like her dad in some way?

355
00:21:36,395 --> 00:21:40,661
Not at all, my master didn't look like
a pervert like him at all!

356
00:21:41,700 --> 00:21:45,192
This is a picture Ms. Sara took
of my master and me together.

357
00:21:47,005 --> 00:21:49,875
Oh my, how gorgeous!
He was very handsome.

358
00:21:49,875 --> 00:21:51,543
I like him. He's my type.

359
00:21:51,543 --> 00:21:54,746
Then why don't you become Sara's mother?

360
00:21:54,746 --> 00:21:58,045
I want Akiko to be my partner.

361
00:21:58,350 --> 00:22:01,887
I'm so sorry that I'm a useless partner.

362
00:22:01,887 --> 00:22:03,354
No!

363
00:22:03,922 --> 00:22:05,389
Sara!

364
00:22:05,924 --> 00:22:08,051
No, you can't be mean to Mr. Saeba!

365
00:22:13,198 --> 00:22:13,732
You too, Ms. Kaori.

366
00:22:13,732 --> 00:22:15,200
You too, Ms. Kaori.
I wanted you to listen to my guitar

367
00:22:15,200 --> 00:22:17,736
I wanted you to listen to my guitar

368
00:22:17,736 --> 00:22:21,695
Ms. Kaori also loves Mr. Saeba!
I wanted to convey my feelings
about you to you

369
00:22:21,973 --> 00:22:27,434
But I couldn't do so

370
00:22:30,215 --> 00:22:37,951
You don't know anything about
this town where I live

371
00:22:38,390 --> 00:22:44,351
You don't know the reason I'm here

372
00:22:46,465 --> 00:22:59,277
If that moment could have colored
the rows of old brick houses

373
00:22:59,277 --> 00:23:02,644
I wouldn't have let you go

374
00:23:03,115 --> 00:23:10,920
While I cross the park shining
in the winter sun

375
00:23:11,256 --> 00:23:17,161
Everyday life is starting

376
00:23:19,564 --> 00:23:27,437
In my mind, time has stopped

377
00:23:27,873 --> 00:23:33,778
And a double-decker bus is passing

378
00:23:39,484 --> 00:23:41,486
I guess Sara hates me.

379
00:23:41,486 --> 00:23:43,021
She read your mind, didn't she?

380
00:23:43,021 --> 00:23:44,890
If so, I have no idea when.

381
00:23:44,890 --> 00:23:46,224
Well, you two need to talk.

382
00:23:46,224 --> 00:23:48,693
The problem won't be solved if you run away
from it. Everything will stay the same.

383
00:23:48,693 --> 00:23:51,062
Oh, no, are you going to the
Nishikujo mansion?

384
00:23:51,062 --> 00:23:54,232
Sara has to become strong by
fighting against evil minds.

385
00:23:54,232 --> 00:23:55,700
Yes, you are right.

386
00:23:55,700 --> 00:23:58,336
Do your best, Sara! I'm going to
give you my bravery.

387
00:23:58,336 --> 00:23:59,504
City Hunter 2:

388
00:23:59,504 --> 00:24:03,108
"Mokkori Everywhere!
Ryo's Mind and an Esper girl (Part 2)"

389
00:24:03,108 --> 00:24:04,871
If you miss it, you won't become strong.

390
00:24:05,143 --> 00:24:09,102
Please look forward to the next episode

